file=AI & Agents/proto/operational/tool/proto-tool-requirements.md · p—t:proto — Tool Requirements=**This file specifies needs; it does not grant them.** Access is configured at deployment (operator/platform; Fleet Charter Rails 1–2 apply; Rail 4 cages every prototype).\n · tb=\| Skill \| Needs \| Why \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| agent-prototype-kit \| file write (prototype folders — quarantined area); registry append via meta \| scaffolds \| · tb=\| eval-first-design \| file read (incumbent behavior for baselines); file write (criteria in manifests) \| frozen criteria \| · tb=\| promote-or-archive-verdict \| file read (frozen criteria, scores); registry state change via meta; anneal ledger append \| verdicts \| · tb=\| rapid-prototyping-method \| sandbox execution (quinn's policy) for rungs 3–4 \| caged builds \| · p—t:proto — Tool Requirements=Prototype folders are a quarantined area — nothing in them is fleet-load-bearing until a PROMOTE proposal lands.\n